        <p>Stop Thief!</p>
        <p>RAN away from the subscriber in the beginning of <date dateType="departure" when="1819-09-01">September</date> last, a negro man named <name xml:id="Jack">Old JACK</name>, aged about 53 years, five feet in height, and very same on account of a broken thigh. The laid Jack is very talkative, polite in his behaviour, and stole a bay mate when he absconded. The said runaway was seen in the neighborhood of <place placeType="location last seen">Chillicothe</place>. Ten Dollars reward will be given for taking him up, or securing him in any jail. Letters directed to <place placeType='pubPlace'>Marietta Post Office</place>, will be attended to.</p> 
        <p><name xml:id="Edward Skelton">EDWARD SKELTON</name>,</p> 
